Description:
A Beautiful Simple cake to Celebrate your TINY Little Birthday... Or ANY Day you want to celebrate a Special Occasion! These cakes are the perfect size for little puppies or small breed babies.
We flavored this cake with several flavors to choose from. It's baked, and then decorated to the colors of your choosing :O)  Please feel free to contact us with specific colors or themes BEFORE Ordering if you don't see a theme listed. 
 The cake size is approx 11" round for the bottom Tier and 8" for the top tier and 3" tall. This cake has served as a Large Cupcake for Shepherd to A Nice size cake for Tinier Breeds. I have personally made this cake for my 3 Puggles and My daughters 2 Pitties and there is still some leftover..... I give them about 2 pieces each.  I then Freeze the rest!
THIS TREAT is NOT Wheat or Gluten free BUT we are excited to NOW have a WHEAT, GLUTEN & GRAIN FREE Recipe .... Option listed is Grain-Wht-Gltn-Free (they dont offer enough characters to spell it all out) and is a 2.50 extra charge.
These Cakes are Hand Detailed and are as Much a work of Art as they are Cookies. 
Laineys Cookies are Wheat, Corn, Gluten, Soy, Sugar, Preservative FREE Cookies with NO Fillers!
ANY Questions or concerns Please FEEL Free to Bark at us! We are ALL Ears. B.O.L.!!
Laineys cookies are SO GOOD you JUST may forget they're for Doggies and eat them Yourself! Go ahead...You won't be the first & Your secret is safe with us!
FLOURS: for MOST COOKIES We are using a Custom blend of flours Including Organic Coconut, Organic White Rice, Potato. These are all Wheat Free, Some are Grain Free and ALL are Gluten Free. For Cakes, Brownies or Donuts We use Pastry Flour... we can make Gluten or Wheat Free.... Just Ask :O)
BAKING TIME: As we are Growing and our Cookies are in More Demand.....Please allow 8 to 10 days (excluding weekends & Holidays) for cooking time BEFORE shipping
ALLERGY ALERT: Although a recipe may NOT contain Peanuts or Mint....They were prepared in a kitchen that HAS!
STORAGE: Since our treats have NO PRESERVATIVES they will not last as long as store bought treats. I would recommend 1 1/2 weeks in a treat jar UNSealed or 4 months in the freezer for Cakes, brownies etc and 2-3 months in a treat jar or 6 months in a freezer for Cookies. Treat these as you would your own baked goods for yourself.
NUTRITION: Even though we use the best ingredients.... it’s recommended that you seek advice from your veterinarian as to what food/ingredients are appropriate for your babies.
SHIPPING: I use US Priority Mail your package should get there in 2-3 days....but its NOT a guarantee! I WANT you to recieve your Cookies AS FAST AS POSSIBLE!! Once I hand them over to the Post Office I can NO LONGER be Responsible for how long Delivery takes I SINCERELY wish I COULD!! PLEASE NOTE: Despite my best efforts in packaging, I can NOT guarantee that you will not have some damage. I will continue to make every effort possible to package these items carefully so that they will arrive safely. We Ask that you Please help in sharing any problems so that we may assess & rectify them!

Product name: Java Junkie Coffee Scrub 4 fl. oz. in MOCHA LATTE
Description:
Our Java Junkie Coffee Scrub will leave your skin feeling soft and looking radiant! Our emulsified exfoliating formula is made using high quality, all natural coffee, which softens skin as it scrubs away dirt and dead skin cells. This formula also contains skin-loving Coconut Oil, Vitamin E oil and Sunflower Seed Oil, making this aromatic exfoliating scrub a luxurious staple in any skin care regime.
4 fl. oz. of our Java Junkie Coffee Scrub is measured by volume and packaged as seen in the photos, sealed in a clear PET plastic jar with a tamper-evident sealed liner printed "SEALED for YOUR PROTECTION ", in your choice of packaging style, with “MOCHA LATTE” fragrance. 
CHOOSE YOUR STYLE: Please make your Packaging Style selection from the drop down menu on the right. If a style preference is not selected, one will be chosen at random.
At Dirty Girl Beauty, we do not add any chemical sulfates, parabens, petrochemicals, mineral oil or phthalates to any of our product formulas. * Our products are tested exclusively on friends, never on animals. *
Directions for Use:
For the best results, always use a sugar scrub while taking a shower. Cleanse and rinse your body as usual, then use our Java Junkie Coffee Scrub to exfoliate and condition your skin. Apply a handful of sugar scrub to wet skin and massage over the entire body, taking care to avoid eyes and other delicate areas. Gently rubbing in a circular motion is most effective as it helps to free ingrown hairs, exfoliate dead skin cells and remove dirt and debris. It is also less abrasive than a back and forth movement. Thoroughly rinse with warm water and pat dry or air dry.
Tips:
It is fine to use bath mitts and gloves as long as they are air dried and kept clean to prevent them from harboring bacteria.
When exfoliating, err on the side of gentle to avoid irritating the skin. Discontinue use if skin irritation occurs.
Immediately after using a scrub, you may want to apply a moisturizer. For added protection, look for products that contain sunflower or sweet almond oils, as well as shea butter.
Your scrub should be stored with the lid tightly closed in a cool dark place to maximize the shelf life.
INCI Label:
INGREDIENTS: Pure Raw Cane Sugar (Sucrose), Sunflower Seed Oil (Helianthus Annuus), Coffee (Coffea Arabica), Coconut Oil (Cocos Nucifera), Emulsifying Wax NF, Stearic Acid NF (vegetable), Vitamin E Oil (Prunus Dulcis (Almond) Oil, Tocopherol), Fragrance oil, Optiphen Preservative (Phenoxyethanol and Caprylyl Glycol)
Coffee & Skin Care:
Many people jump-start their day with a cup of coffee, but did you know that coffee also has a number of perks for your skin, from treating redness and inflammation to reducing the appearance of cellulite?
Incorporating coffee in your skin care regime can help you achieve evenly toned, smoother skin. Coffee containing caffeine is a rich source of antioxidants. Your body is a war-zone between two types of molecules: free radicals and antioxidants. Free radicals damage healthy cells, while antioxidants work to protect against free radical damage. Antioxidants can neutralize the damaging effects of free radicals on the inner layer of skin, which is often reflected in age spots and wrinkles. In short, antioxidants help bolster your skin’s natural defenses.
The caffeine in coffee dehydrates skin cells in a good way by energizing them, causing the release of sodium, potassium and water, thus helping skin appear smoother. Because of this, caffeine is often utilized in cellulite reduction. Caffeine has potent anti-inflammatory properties, which can assist in reducing puffiness. When applied topically, the caffeine in coffee also works as a vasodilator, which means that it constricts and tightens the blood vessels in the skin, thereby improving skin texture.
Additionally, ground coffee is a natural and organic exfoliant. Regular exfoliation of the skin removes residual dirt and dead skin cells, stimulates the production of new skin cells, and revitalizes your skin. Freshly exfoliated skin absorbs moisture much more effectively.
Learn more about our Featured Ingredient: Vitamin E Oil!
Vitamin E Oil:
Vitamin E oil is naturally occurring oil, which is soluble in lipid and is non-enzymatic. The skin benefits of vitamin E come from its antioxidant properties. Antioxidants remove free radicals — the unstable compounds that damage the cell structure. Vitamin E oil can help smooth the appearance of wrinkles by boosting collagen production, a connective tissue that keeps skin elastic. It supports new skin cell growth and helps speed up cell regeneration. Vitamin E oil also has anti-inflammatory properties. As the epidermis layer of the skin absorbs vitamin E, it can be used for treating sunburn or acne. Vitamin E oil prevents water loss from the skin and helps it to retain its natural moisture. Vitamin E oil can help dull-looking, dry skin look healthier and fresher.

Product name: Hairpin Legs for DIY Furniture: Sizes 17"-20"
Description:
Hairpin legs are a classic design that seems to go with any décor which makes these an excellent choice for DIY furniture projects. One of the best things about these legs is they are super strong and we actually use a hairpin leg table for a work table. They hold upwards of 3 to 400 lbs easily. The bar is 3/8, the plate is 4.75 long. Each leg comes with screws and a floor protector. We sell by the leg, so 1 equals 1 leg. Shipping charges include recyclable/recycled fiber packaging paper and FedEx home delivery. Home delivery costs a bit more but they do deliver on Saturdays in most areas. Shipping is 12 a leg and 1 for each additional leg. 
*Please note, any legs that stand above 25 inches have a tendency to wobble. This is the nature of steel so they may hold 500LBs but they wobble. This can pose a problem for dinner tables or writing desks where it is important for the table to be steady. 
 We try to be competitive by offering maximum value and quality. We offer more holes for the mounting plate for optimum security to your wood top. We also bevel and fillet weld using an industrial welder that is probably over the top but we make sure the welds are very strong. We do not do hidden welds or otherwise cosmetic welding as this is not ideal for loadbearing applications. Please beware of sellers offering such welding, it is unsuitable for table legs. This is the reason many legs from the 50's fall apart because they were not welded for long term use. This may be one of the few times when saying, "they don't make them how they used to" is a good thing.
Each leg comes with self drilling screws and a floor protector so they are ready to go right out of the box. When ordering, please select the number of legs you would like with the size you need. If you are looking for another size, you can access those sizes in other listings in our main store. 
The mounting plate is a little under 4.75 long and has five 1/4 inch holes with the majority of holes around the bars for maximum stability. Our legs have a slight angle at 10 degrees. We offer a darker grey (hot rolled) or raw(cold rolled) steel from mills we hand select from right here in the US. The dark grey is more rustic and worn looking steel which can have varying greys and browns with very minimal rust spots and pitting. Please select this option for a more rustic look. We also offer a raw steel that is perfect for polishing, painting or patinas. This looks a lot like stainless steel. 
Our legs are raw and can have oil, dirt, grime and other varieties. We do a light wipe down of each leg. We do not sell heavily rusted or otherwise gouged legs. We recommend that some sort of top coat should be applied whether its paint, wax or a little polyurethane. Wax is your best bet and a giant tub can be purchased for around 6 at any hardware store. I recommend Johnson's Paste wax. We would recommend just wiping them down with a rag and giving them a light waxing. 
Please check your address when ordering, Philly Fabrication cannot be responsible for items delivered to the wrong address. Please contact us if you live in Hawaii, Alaska, Puerto Rico before ordering to get a shipping quote. 
How to Finish the Raw Steel: Take steel wool/scotchbrite pad and scrub the steel until the look you want is created. You can use a high zero steel wool to create a great polish. If you are looking to paint, please see the many tutorials online on how to paint steel. Please keep in mind finish the raw steel comes with is good on its own. 
Please contact us for information about any of what we have on this site. Please ask us anything about sizing, materials, etc. We are happy to help. Philly Fabrication is not responsible for wrong sizing so please contact us for any guidance any project, we will offer any support we can give. 
Local Pickup: Please contact us with the finish you want, grey or raw and the size you need. 
All products are made in Philadelphia, Pa with US steel.

Product name: ON SALE QUEEN Comforter - perfect comfort,for all seasons, handmade wool comforter, luxury bedding, organic duvet insert, housewarming gift
Description:
LISTING: 
Queen size, all seasons warmth, all-natural handpicked virgin wool filled comforter. 
Chemically untreated wool provides the perfect four-season comfort no matter where you live. That's because wool is naturally thermo-regulating – it's insulating in the cold, and cool and breathable when it's warm. Feel comfortable and stay warm all year round. 
"Good Night" products are handmade, starting from sheep farming to the final product. 
DETAILS:
• Dimensions - 90"x90" 
• Fabric - 100% cotton sateen, Oeko-tex certified
• Filling - 100% all-natural handpicked virgin wool that has not been treated with any harmful chemicals or additives, 450 GSM.
FABRIC COLOR:
All items pictured in our shop are in "Off White". Before ordering other color please contact us to make sure we have the chosen fabric. We are trying to do our best to represent exact fabric colors on pictures but color may slightly vary due to screen resolution and digital photography.
CARE:
Dry cleaning is the best way to clean a wool comforter. In between the dry cleaning, a good shake in open air is adequate. Also ventilate if a natural wool smell seems too strong. Protect your comforter with a duvet cover, which keeps it clean and prolongs its life. It's much more preferable to frequently clean the duvet cover than to have to constantly clean the comforter.
Matching wool filled pillows: 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/248373867/queen-size-organic-wool-filled-pillow?ref=shop_home_active_2
https://www.etsy.com/listing/248482750/queen-size-organic-wool-filled-pillow?ref=shop_home_active_2
HOW IT IS MADE:
Industry processes wool in huge quantities and uses technological advances for that. They wash wool with harsh and efficient detergents. Here machines as human hands work which can't have a contact with these agents. Carbonising, bleaching, polymer coating and other are conventional wool processing methods. The way it passes damages the wool fiber and loses the major part of the unique features. 
Our products use wool untreated by chemicals, just hand washed using natural soap. The chosen method of processing is much heavier but it ensures high-quality and is environment friendly. Hand washed wool preserves the lanolin, which helps to ensure its softness and waviness. Wool is not only the least vulnerable, but also is pleasant to cuddle up. It's time and physical strength consuming work. But the easier way - to buy industrially processed wool is not pointed in our plans. Other way, the idea to share truthful wishes from the countryside would lose its meaning.
100% HANDCRAFTED:
"Good Night" products are handmade, starting from sheep farming to the final product. Sheep shearing at the farm takes place over a few days and is an interesting sight. Also of interest is 'wool carding', a mechanical process that disentangles, cleans and intermixes fibers to produce a continuous web or sliver suitable for subsequent processing. Finally wool webs lies on a luxury cotton cloth, and professional seamstresses hands turns it to lovely bedding

Product name: Coconut Vanilla Vegan Aluminum Free  Cream Deodorant
Description:
Coconut VanillaVegan Aluminum Free  Cream Deodorant
 ****HEAT WARNING! Warm weather will keep the deodorant in a more liquid state.  This is natural due to the high content of coconut oil, which melts at very low temperatures.  This is normal and does not affect the deodorant at all.  If it separates, just give it a quick stir before using.  It is recommended to keep it in the fridge during the warmer months if you prefer it to be more solid.  
A recent study has shown that it takes 10 seconds for our skin to absorb into our body what we put on to it.  Have you ever looked at the ingredients list on commercial deodorants?  Do you really want to put all those chemicals on your skin and into your body???  I use only natural ingredients - aluminum-free baking soda helps absorb moisture and odor, arrowroot powder aids in moisture absorbtion, kaolin clay also helps with moisture and odor elimination.  Coconut oil has long been known as a natural deodorizer.  
This is a deodorant formula only - although it does help hinder excess moisture, it will not stop it.  It was created to effectively control odor all day long.  If you've never used all natural deodorant before, its best to give your body a few days to get used to it.  Your body needs to adjust to the changes from using chemicals to going all natural.
This listing is for one 2oz shallow jar of  deodorant cream.  To use it, scoop out a pea sized amount and rub into your underarm area.  There are no artificial hardeners in this deodorant - it will soften  at contact with your skin, making it quite easy to apply.  If it seems too soft, pop it into the fridge for a few minutes. Product name: Bronze Guitar Pick Handmade with I Pick You - Custom Guitar Pick GP009
Description:
I pick you is fresh out of my studio more beautiful than ever and now available in bronze. Custom cut in our own studio from 20 gauge bronze and stamped by hand with I Pick You, this bronze guitar pick rocks out the love for any occasion 
To impress with stunning contrast, a dark patina has been added to the lettering, before burnishing the bronze, and finishing the metal with a soft buffing wheel for a radiant bronze glow.
The guitar pick features filed edges and polished surfaces to give your strings and fingers a little love. 
Bronze is an amazing metal with a more metallic sound quality when used as a pick. In fact there are musicians that specifically seek out bronze picks to add a unique tone quality to their music. I made this guitar pick from 20 gauge bronze as a medium weight pick according to the Wikipedia guitar pick scale, so that the pick would easier to use and play than the 18 gauge or thick metal. Of course, I can accept custom orders for 18 gauge thick and heavy picks or lightweight 22 gauge picks. The 20 gauge feels just right with a perfect bright tone.
This guitar pick measures about 1.3 inch long by 1.2 wide and has a very solid feel at a comfortable weight. If you would like a custom size, personalized stamping, or your very own custom bronze guitar pick, don't hesitate to contact me. Move out of the Stone Age and into the Bronze Age with a shiny new bronze pick. Thanks for visiting my Etsy shop.. Nici
Please don't hesitate to contact us or call our shop at 575.737.8521 with questions and requests.

Product name: SaleToday Small Vintage Wooden Bobbin Industrial Era Ratcheted Spools Organize Display Home Decor
Description:
Small vintage textile mill braider bobbins, all with wooden gear-like ratcheted tops AND bottoms. 
The braider bobbin was used to produce a uniform braid in a 'maypole' style wrap, often water was used to power the braiding machines. Each bobbin is 4 1/2 inches tall and 1 3/4 inches wide at the top. Trim shown is for display only, not for sale. Ratcheted bobbins are scored along the shaft (in last photo) when last of the yarn or fiber is removed from the bobbin with a hand knife.
The wooden bobbin is a bit of textile history. Made to last. Victorian textile mills developed wooden bobbins and spools to organize the threads on their looms, completely transforming the way textiles were produced during the industrial revolution. 
An enduring way to organize your twine, ribbons and trims. Something to re-use, not toss. Or killer chess pieces for the serious textile hound. ;-)
Please note: As always, I quickly refund any shipping over-payments, beyond a dollar, without being asked. Haven't had one complaint yet!

Product name: 5 Pack assorted Tillandsia Ionantha air plants - Rainforest Alliance Donation Item!
Description:
This pack will include 5 easy-to-care-for Tillandsia ionantha species only air plants.  Tillandsia air plants are low maintenance and high reward.  Give them light and an occasional water spray and they will turn beautiful shades of pink, red, yellow, and orange.  In no time at all, you will enjoy a beautiful, bright bloom! Better yet, the excitement starts long before blooming time for many of these, as they grow pups throughout their lifespan. Care Instructions will be provided, but take care to tailor your routine to your specific environment.
Sizing and Appearance: You will receive plants between 1.25 and 3 inches in height. They will be a random selection from our greenhouse.  Color/Blush is not guaranteed but will be provided when it is available. Blush is an air plant's response to sun exposure or stage of bloom cycle.  Color can be encouraged by sun exposure once you receive the plants. Ionanthas are all the same SUB-SPECIES, so they are going to naturally have a similar appearance.  You are receiving 3 different varieties, even if they look similar.  If you need help identifying the varieties, please send a photo once they arrive.  If you wish to have 3 very distinct looking plants, please consider our other 3 assorted tillandsia pack.
Guess What! A portion of the proceeds from the purchase of this item will go to our monthly donations to the Rainforest Alliance TREES program to support sustainable business practices and responsible collection practices. 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please Read:
RETURNS/REFUNDS: We do not accept returns for any reason. Plants that are delayed or not delivered by USPS, or packages with incorrect shipping addresses will not be eligible for refunds or replacements, Unless the buyer has purchased priority mail or faster mail service.  Please consider using priority mail service or buying shipping insurance to protect your purchase.
SHIPPING: All orders received by 10 am (PST), Monday through Thursday, are shipped next business day via the postal service requested at checkout. Weekends and postal holidays are excluded. We do not ship on Mondays. We May occasionally increase our shipping turnaround during times of heavy traffic. Please contact the shop if plants are needed by a specific date. 
IN HOT WEATHER: If your order will encounter temperatures over 70 degrees at any point in transit, Please select USPS Priority Mail or faster as your shipping method. Do not let your plants remain outdoors for any period of time. If plants arrive damaged due to heat exposure and this protection was not purchased, we will not refund or replace your order. Damage from heat exposure will result in brown plants or completely dried and dead plants. 
IN COLD WEATHER: If your order will experience temperatures near or below freezing at any point during transit, Please select the heat pack and priority mail shipping option at checkout. Do not allow your plants to sit outdoors for any length of time after delivery.  Purchases made without this protection that result in damaged plants, will not be eligible for refund or replacement. Damage from cold exposure will result in brown and/or mushy plants.

Product name: Rose Gold Stud Earrings, Rose Gold Druzy Earrings, Rose Gold Earrings, Rose Gold Post Earring, Rosegold Druzy Earring,Gold Stud Earring,10MM
Description:
THE DETAILS:
Rose gold jewelry is a staple in any jewelry collection, and these lovely stud earrings are no exception! Rose gold is right on trend, and is a modern neutral that can match almost anything. The earrings feature resin rose gold druzy cabochons set on rose-gold plated studs! Dress them up or down! The earrings come with soft rubber earring backs, perfect for those with sensitive ears!
**IMPORTANT** DRUZY CARE:
Rose gold gets its rose color from the addition of copper. Copper IS susceptible to tarnish. When not wearing the rose gold earrings, It is EXTREMELY IMPORTANT to ALWAYS store them in the included bag, to prevent tarnish. Also store them on the included jewelry tag, to prevent scratches or damage to the resin druzy.
POSTS AND SETTING:
The setting (metal surrounding the druzy) and the earring post are made of brass, plated with a rose gold finish.
DIMENSIONS:
Diameter of the druzy is 10MM. Including the metal setting, the diameter is 12mm.
